			},
			#name : #'newCellAt:at:size:',
			#protocol : #'as yet unclassified',
			#sourceCode : 'newCellAt: i at: j size: unTamaño\r"Create a cell for position (i,j) and add it to my on-screen\rrepresentation at the appropriate screen position. Answer the\rnew cell"\r| c origin |\r\tc := NOCell new.\r\tc setTamaño: unTamaño.\r\torigin := self innerBounds origin.\r\tself addMorph: c.\r\tc position: ((i - 1) * c width) @ ((j - 1) * c height) + origin.\r\tc mouseAction: [ \r\t\tc isOn ifTrue: [ self disminuir] \r\t\tifFalse: [ self aumentar].\r\t\tc toggleState.\r\t\t].\r\t^c',
